Project Vision--

-Smart Personal Finance Analyzer-

A data-driven personal finance platform that helps users manage expenses, analyze spending behavior, predict future budgets, detect unusual transactions, and receive AI-powered financial insights.

Think of it as combining features from Mint, YNAB, and Google Analytics for personal finances.

Tech Stack

Backend: Java 21 + Spring Boot
Database: PostgreSQL
Frontend: Thymeleaf + Bootstrap (we can migrate to React later if you want)
Charts: Chart.js
ML: Python (Linear Regression)
Build Tool: Maven
Version Control: Git
